# Lingmo OS System Include Files
#
# This directory contains system header files for C/C++ development.
# Use these headers when building software for @DISTRO_NAME@.
#
# Usage in Makefiles/CMake:
#   CFLAGS += -I/system/include
#   CXXFLAGS += -I/system/include
#
# Standards compliance: POSIX.1-2008, C11, C++17
#
# @DISTRO_NAME@ @VERSION@
# Build: @BUILD_VER@
